  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300\u000072F (150\u000073C).",
    "In a large Dutch oven, melt the butter over medium heat. Add the short ribs and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the flour, baking powder, salt, and pepper to the pot, stirring to combine.",
    "Transfer the pot to the preheated oven and braise the short ribs for 2\u0000 hours, or until tender.",
    "Meanwhile, prepare the madeleine cake mix according to the package instructions.",
    "After the short ribs have finished braising, remove the pot from the oven and stir in the prepared horseradish and chopped parsley.",
    "Transfer the short ribs to a plate and top each one with a madeleine cake round.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!"
